                Imminet Leoni Virgo caeles<lb break="no" n="2"/>ti situ spicifera iusti in<lb break="no" n="3"/>ventrix urbium conditrix <lb n="4"/>ex quis muneribus nosse con<lb break="no" n="5"/>tigit deos ergo eadem mater divum <lb n="6"/>Pax Virtus Ceres Dea Syria <lb n="7"/>lance vitam et iura pensitans <lb n="8"/>in caelo visum Syria sidus edi<lb break="no" n="9"/>dit Libyae colendum inde <lb n="10"/>cuncti didicimus <lb n="11"/>ita intellexit numine inductus <lb n="12"/>tuo Marcus Caecilius Do<lb break="no" n="13"/>natianus militans tribunus <lb n="14"/>in praefecto dono principis
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Metrum: Iambische senarii.</p>
